**Wager Recipient** | Extra Miscellaneous

__Basics__
The devil can wager someone each day, granting them access to the wager channel where they can communicate with the devil and select the option to use one of several powers.

__Details__
During the day the devil may select a player to offer a wager to. The following night the player will be added to the wager channel, and will leave at the start of the following day. In the wager channel they have the option to use one of several powers, see $i wager for more information. 
